+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0 OR BSD-2-Clause
+/*
+ * LRNG proc and sysctl interfaces
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2016 - 2021, Stephan Mueller <smueller@chronox.de>
